Ambani's Reliance Communications, Reliance Infrastructure Fall in Mumbai

-- B y   H a r i   G o v i n d
-- 
2011-02-14T03:51:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/ambani-s-reliance-communications-reliance-infrastructure-fall-in-mumbai.html
  Reliance Communications Ltd . and
Reliance Infrastructure Ltd., owned by billionaire Anil Ambani,
fell in Mumbai after his group said Indian federal investigators
examined some of its officials.  Reliance Communications dropped 2.7 percent to 94.5 rupees
at 9:18 a.m. local time and Reliance Infrastructure declined 0.8
percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hari Govind at 
 hgovind@bloomberg.net  